725001f-a.title: Queens: 11th Avenue - E. 144th Street.
725001f-a.text:
11th Avenue, east from 144th Street, showing the thoroughfare
as a dirt rocd through the woods.
P.L.Sperr  March 3, 1932

725874f-a.title: Queens: 144th Street - 11th Avenue
725874f-a.text:
144th Street, at 11th Avenue (vantage point). Shown are two views of the salt meadows and glacial boulders in the
willage of Malba.
P. L' Snerr  March 3, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
